    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <date>January 14th 67</date>
            </p>
            <p>My dear <addressee>Mr Leeser</addressee></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Your letter of the <date>10th</date>
                <lb/><placeName>Charleston</placeName>‚Äù has just been<lb/> received, we are very
                glad<lb/> to hear that your voice<lb/> has improved, but too<lb/> think that you are
                very<lb/> imprudent to come north<lb/> so soon; the weather is very<lb/> severe here
                now &amp; the<lb/> sleighing is very good.</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>Mamma<add>?</add> says that<lb/> she is very anxious to<lb/> see you &amp; can
                hardly<lb/> wait for you to come<lb/> home; we have been quite<lb/> busy getting the
                girls ripe<add>?</add><lb/> for a Ball; a Hebrew Ball<lb/> to be given at the
                Academy<lb/> of music on the <date>22nd</date> &amp;<lb/> complimentary tickets
                have<lb/> been sent here for yourself<lb/> &amp; two ladies ‚Äî Mamma</p>
            <pb n="3"/>
            <p>bought very pretty dresses<lb/> at <persName>Pesea's</persName> &amp; this
                morning<lb/> I went up to the dressmakers<lb/> with <persName>Sophie</persName>
                &amp; <persName>Bertha</persName> to see<lb/> about the ‚Äú<hi rend="underline"
                    >making</hi>.‚Äù I<lb/> suppose that you will be<lb/> home in time for the
                Ball.<lb/> Mamma has been very<lb/> sick but is now better; she<lb/> sends you her
                love, &amp;c.<lb/>
                <persName>Martha Jay<add>?</add></persName> is now here<lb/> making us a
                    <add>?</add></p>
            <pb n="4"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <persName role="author">Miss E L Cozens</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <date>Jany 14, 1867</date>
            </p>
            <p>I intend to pay $75 to <persName>Mr<lb/> Milert<add>?</add></persName> &amp; $50 to
                    <add>?</add> on<lb/>
                <date>Wednesday</date>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">There is nothing new to<lb/> write; <persName>Rev Mr
                    Jacobson</persName> wishes you<lb/> to make him a visit in
                    <placeName>Wash-<lb/>ington</placeName>; he wrote to <sic>enquire</sic><lb/>
                about your health &amp; I answered<lb/> the letter &amp; sent him some
                Occi-<lb/>dents that he desired to have<lb/> Good bye, All send love</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Yours Sincerely</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <persName role="author">E L Cozens</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
